      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORMY DAY (6) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from three starts. In the money last time at Murray Bridge Straight (17.05) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a half a length second. With a clean break looks hard to beat. BINNAWAY WARRIOR (1) continues to race in super honest form hitting the frame at 30 of 55 starts runs and has won two of last three, the latest winning (22.60) over 400m at Mt Gambier. Has a strong record at this journey including three wins. Rates a winning chance on best. WEBLEC PRINCE (8) failed to feature last start after missing the jump at Angle Park, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at Angle Park (30.33) beating Compton Gypsy in a Special conditions race on February 5. Is yet to taste defeat in two starts from this draw. Should be about the money. ATTENTION SEEKER (2) was below best last time at Angle Park (30.98) in a Grade 6, finishing a 7 length fifth. Already a winner from this draw.",
